c855-c2a3-4db1-8ee6-7e8ac11ae076\" style=\"color:#555555;\">함께 제작하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d056bd01-4b14-4df8-b545-590d0e11dc4e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-39abce52-f809-4e62-9880-a55b5f07b1ea\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-825185f6-2168-466e-a86a-8af7268488e8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:692px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223806822041/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f97b4554-9f3c-4cf8-8c10-949f911b5a47\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2d77a0fe-eb79-4103-a702-4244c0941ed4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-da4fd645-e839-4f94-b5bc-55738331ce00\" style=\"color:#555555;\">교정을 진행하고 최종 파일은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c481c145-2b4b-4d77-8a37-3c7e3ec79d3e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c0de2296-0651-42d2-96b2-64ea5422a2eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">png 파일로 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-91803cfd-de79-4adb-87e7-d126097e455b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-42317bda-7f20-41a2-9667-d9351fe7b07f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그러면 다음과 같이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e2081e94-0795-4851-b4dc-6781af15c508\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d1dc442f-4b72-4f59-8ef0-626144960dbf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">카톡이나 문자로 디지털 형식 전송이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5980c593-b8e1-4c8d-8415-5c426e875be4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-de8dcec5-33a5-42ec-8943-8b592b38c016\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-71b73280-81a1-401c-a21c-4ab4ededbc16\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-01f478bb-99bb-4e72-81b3-504070699f54\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d3503b3b-e4e2-4057-8123-0b5c417ed7a6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:430px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223806822041/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-189df38f-58e8-43de-8c6c-801c05d27e1c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-75bdc4a7-1f0d-412e-820e-2c8fd67d52dd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aabc5d0b-ca08-40f4-81cf-bc0804b5c613\" style=\"color:#555555;\">카톡으로 보냈을 때의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1bfb4a25-9d4f-4160-ab0c-fa764c412982\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4ff5137c-f727-4519-b225-f846354358e0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사이즈도 거의 맞춰서 작업하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8157022b-c2fb-4318-b2c6-84107f7bc588\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5ee4b626-9926-44b0-abbe-6222b8395ee0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-ef1eb948-4f56-414b-815f-bc4a1571b152\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-baa52e19-fc2e-472d-bff2-8c8f557a02d0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-4bdace7d-9648-43da-acc9-a78d4598c810\" style=\"\">디지털용 포스터 제작 조건</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-932b0b2d-b8c0-433b-9b5c-00b31b7df3b5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-18de6dc0-8893-4171-9b5b-0dd74b061105\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ac007ee4-707a-466b-92ee-f6369f81febd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">카톡으로 보내는 디지털용 포스터 제작 조건이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c6438599-f598-474c-881d-c0f86d376885\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4ea15cc6-d1fe-4703-a241-a429d66361ac\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제작 조건이 붙는 이유는 오로지 단가 부분입니다. 디지털이라는 특성상 수정이 무한으로 가능하고 단발성이 아니기 때문에 디자인 비용에 대한 휘발성, 단발성 여부가 비용을 결정하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4b865219-ae7f-4afb-a68f-1191b3c1db56\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9c9afc85-9907-40b8-9af8-87805dde1395\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c4eef947-4a5c-4e4e-9aa2-0d67b343fddc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e896ea6b-243e-4037-a77d-820599d04a7a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이제 여러분이 포스터를 만드는 데 정기적으로 제작하는 포스터라면 가장 저렴한 비용을 자랑하는 (주)파파스컴퍼니과 상의하십시오.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1dc17657-1df1-4b6e-804b-b21540b63110\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8382ef26-6ac2-4f2f-8d5b-e08b5aaeacdf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-edb34bec-1a16-44f0-973e-5e1be68c9252\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9d50c8c3-2861-4a55-9141-bbd93a5ac2d8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">위의 예시는 정기적인 골프 모임을 하는 관광회사의 정기적인 이벤트 포스터를 디지털로 제작합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-246d1051-7682-41f0-b09c-62d87fcb3bb9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e8e20efd-f826-49a2-8453-2c80bdd83658\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-74398d6e-059e-478e-8246-8e36920bf6c0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bf32316a-1ed7-4f90-9565-8f39d81f43e6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그 비용은 공개할 수 없지만 고객 여러분이 생각하시는 포스터 디자인 비용보다 훨씬 저렴하게 공급하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-85f6dbbf-2d72-4c7a-a4fc-53ccaa345259\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d09acc89-0a67-4939-b99f-d75f721e0db0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-af4aa8e1-af65-45f8-9b45-f6504222dbf7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5d9e3c42-b25f-4afe-b5c2-a5c936a82953\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그런 이유는 두 가지 때문입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ea3d3a56-2067-4000-b6cd-bffd6f7b2859\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-46101260-6981-4b2e-9a14-3d4849516eea\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-56a15f69-5d2a-4ba5-a379-308df671d7d1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1464a197-e5da-43d5-a7d8-3bb7d20756af\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하나는 실제 인쇄를 하지 않기 때문에 원가는 디자인 인건비뿐입니다. 그래서 그 인건비를 가장 저렴한 비용으로 산정하여 공급합니다. 물론 요즘은 인건비 싸움입니다. 인건비가 가장 비싸기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ee9b74a6-3262-4f5d-a194-cb16cd601fb0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9ac6ccba-6d3e-4ed6-b9e4-90f203e50a7f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4563574e-ea9c-4451-b7e6-dc9575b936ba\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-735819f1-276d-41e8-ac07-4b3a64cda7b3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-876b1062-592c-431e-8c93-46082bf71721\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니은 고객님이 납득할 수 있는 가장 합리적인 인건비를 제시</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b8b1b48d-9339-46a2-b4db-6fea374167e8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-569436d6-c7f6-4a36-b733-47eb290af29a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-17da8253-65ff-4667-9de2-b6febe861f3c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-143eb66a-0ff2-4798-927f-a81a4069663d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-39db3e87-fd22-4e78-bbf7-e8aaccfaf5bd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">두 번째는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-0ec40e9c-4393-4d0f-a1ef-00ee80e992f7\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>정기적인 발주</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-259bd4f2-4690-4c0e-8d9a-6765f2594f87\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다. 일회성 포스터는 기본적으로 디자인 비용이 몇십만 원을 호가합니다. 그건 당연합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e48a1959-a8d3-42ea-85d4-426035390cce\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2b08078a-df41-4359-99ec-573729a8645c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3ca1d9d1-fcf3-4453-970c-180d7d5067e1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d5735b06-e9b6-4391-b467-b475d5c182a1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 (주)파파스컴퍼니이 제시하는 디지털 포스터는 정기적인 발주를 근거로 템플릿 화하여 작업비를 최소화합니다. 물론 이 부분은 사전에 고객과의 약속에 근거합니다. 계속적인 정기 발주를 담보로 그 템플릿을 (주)파파스컴퍼니이 투자하고 이후 발주부터는 새로운 레이아웃의 신규 디자인이 아닌 기존 템플릿을 업그레이드하는 수준이라고 이해해 주시면 좋겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b3a57a55-cd27-4860-919e-3afa22505195\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-44556610-035b-4b6b-9843-7f93c3006888\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-81bb4501-75c4-4c78-b050-e00a0b209ab7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cff5bf21-577c-4a48-bce8-9722705c2fdd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 작업을 하면 고객과 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 서로 윈윈하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-dfb0ea2b-84e4-4b47-89e8-270d343cc45f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1bcbce4c-0cac-4224-a15d-bbb31fba6d80\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ebbb6e7c-b60f-4172-9ee5-3dd502025a36\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-95b0803c-afeb-425a-bbfd-0cf7d41c9b1e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객은 고객대로 저렴하게 디지털 포스터를 제작할 수 있고 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 정기적인 주문의 수주를 받을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ba2f2a2c-758a-4d7e-bcb4-7b1ea3e632c6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223806822041/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8273b74b-71ef-4133-8f56-9284df199d2a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-717cb21a-50d7-4ed6-8fd5-83f6dffb8b44\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e7c16989-7e7c-4978-bda8-0bcb580572b6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-93ca3e1e-d347-40b0-a3dc-8a5e35dbb025\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:664px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<im